title: CreativeMarket - Crisp Impact - 420 Lightroom Presets
description:
In a Nutshell

    84 crisp effects
    5 strengths per effect = 420 Lightroom presets total
    Minimal settings
    Does not overwrite basic tonal adjustments
    Human-readable tone curve

Crisp Impact is your recipe for subtly clean and crisp images. They give your photos a sutble grungy look with muted colors and sharp edges. All of the effects can be faded from light to strong in five levels.

These Lightroom presets are compatible with Adobe Lightroom 4, 5, 6 and CC. They work great with JPG/RAW images and are partially compatible with video clips (Clarity setting is not compatible with video clips). Tested and compatible with LR Toolkit.
